reviews.text:
One of the best Italian Restaurants I have been to. Fresh and authentic food and ingredients, great service and good vibes. 
Better than many restaurants in Italy.
Excellent Italian comfort food! Location is not ideal but it's worth the detour for their pizza and starters. Staff is very friendly and welcoming too!

Incredible experience. Visiting Hong Kong and needed a relief from all of the traditional food. Perfect break- with fantastic atmosphere and amazing food! Lovely! Was in Italy last year and made us feel like we got 2 vacations!

Small fancy place, brilliant Italian pizza.
Burrata e Parma, Green Salad must try!
Seats are not cozy though.
Small little shop. Real nice pizza ! Staff are great. Great restaurants

reviews.text:
This place is an absolute eye opener. It was below our hotel and linked with our rail station. Yes, where in the UK would you get a huge complex like this dedicated to a huge travel hub, its crazy.
The prices where excellent, something for everyone, huge amount of passenger footfall but the size of the place is just huge.
Every train, every taxi and every bus was absolutely on time.
Very easy to navigate around the city as there are lots of street signs as well as a very efficient public transport system. Food is really great, too!
You can find ferry’s to Macau, Nanshan, Lian hua San, and many more places to mainland china. There are many brands outlets store are there. Good place to shop.

reviews.author_name: Martin C. Drot de Gourville Chazarène
reviews.text: It is most enchanting city of the world... always sleepness
This place goes on forever.  Wear your walking shoes and just enjoy yourself.

reviews.text: 最好吃的義大利菜在這裡💕

One of the best Italian Restaurants I have been to. Fresh and authentic food and ingredients, great service and good vibes. 
Better than many restaurants in Italy.
Excellent Italian comfort food! Location is not ideal but it's worth the detour for their pizza and starters. Staff is very friendly and welcoming too!

Complimenti! 
This is the place all italians coming to HK should visit, just like where we Chinese will go when we visit Rome.
You know everyone needs some comfort food when you are travelling far!
Pancetta, bufala, acciughe, and my favourite gorgonzola, remind me of the days in Puglia with fresh burrata
A taste of real Italian flavour!
Grazie, Marzia! 

口味非常正宗的意大利餐廳
如果你未去過意大利 可以黎呢度試試真意大利菜 材料傳統
店內全英文招待 不過唔洗緊張 店主Marzia好friendly 一句ciao會令佢好開心 可以請佢介紹一下menu
（見到有評語話服務態度麻麻 但留意返意大利人係比較直同快 唔會慢慢同你轉彎抹角）
兩個人食太飽無叫antipasti
但叫咗個有burrata嘅pasta
burrata係一款內裡有cream嘅mozzarella（留意呢個mozzarella唔係超市一包包乾乾哋嘅美式芝士）
真係新鮮白色一個blob嘅
口味清新
叫咗speck＆gorgonzola pizza同
有興趣可以試siciliana pizza非香港常見但其實係好傳統嘅口味
必試真tiramisu 唔係切件蛋糕 唔好甜品嘅朋友都讚
알바하시는 분도 너무 친절하시고 음식 맛도 좋았고 양도 많았어요~ 분위기도 좋은 피자집이라 한국에서 여행오신 분들 모두에게 추천할게요!! 홍콩 여행 다시 오면 또 올 것 같아요!! 포장도 가능하니까 드시다가 남으면 포장해가세요~! 테이크아웃도 가능해요!
